{"data": [{"id": "4742172", "title": "2020 Bulkers: Paid A 16% Dividend Yield In The Past 12 Months", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bulk Carrier Ship Offloading Cargo By Crane for Processing\" data-id=\"1412530473\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1150px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">CloudVisual</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4714852-2020-bulkers-smart-asset-sales-cut-net-debt-by-40-percent\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4714852-2020-bulkers-smart-asset-sales-cut-net-debt-by-40-percent\" target=\"_blank\">Back in August</a>, I rated the shares of 2020 Bulkers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TTBKF\" title=\"2020 Bulkers Ltd.\" target=\"_blank\">OTCPK:TTBKF</a>) to be a \"hold.\" A wise decision (hindsight is always 20/20) as the total return of TTBKF was a negative 10% while the performance of the S&amp;P 500 (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1412530473/image_1412530473.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742172-2020-bulkers-paid-a-16-percent-dividend-yield-in-the-past-12-months", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 19:40:00"}, {"id": "4742721", "title": "Oracle And Broadcom Are Top Names Reporting Results As Earning Season Winds Down", "description": "<p><span>Get ahead of the market by subscribing to Seeking Alpha's Wall Street Week Ahead, a preview of key events scheduled for the coming week. The newsletter keeps you informed of the biggest stories set to make headlines, including upcoming IPOs, investor days, earnings reports, and conference presentations.</span></p> <p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e7b2c158-7fff-b4a7-e735-04841c6e3623\"></span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Investors next week will be looking for the print on November inflation on Wednesday, a week before the Federal Reserve\u2019s next meeting. Meanwhile, the European Union will release its latest data on industrial production for October. </span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The earnings season window continues, with the number of releases coming to a trickle. The big names scheduled to report include Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>), Adobe (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADBE\" title=\"Adobe Inc.\">ADBE</a>), Broadcom (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AVGO\" title=\"Broadcom Inc.\">AVGO</a>), Costco Wholesale (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COST\" title=\"Costco Wholesale Corporation\">COST</a>), Toll Brothers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TOL\" title=\"Toll Brothers, Inc.\">TOL</a>), and Ciena (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIEN\" title=\"Ciena Corporation\">CIEN</a>). </span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>Earnings spotlight:</span></strong><span> Monday, December 9 - Oracle, Toll Brothers, and Casey\u2019s General Stores (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CASY\" title=\"Casey's General Stores, Inc.\">CASY</a>). </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\"><span>See the full earnings calendar</span></a><span>.</span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>Earnings spotlight:</span></strong><span> Tuesday, December 10 - AutoZone (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AZO\" title=\"AutoZone, Inc.\">AZO</a>), Ferguson Enterprises (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FERG\" title=\"Ferguson Enterprises Inc.\">FERG</a>), GameStop (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GME\" title=\"GameStop Corp.\">GME</a>), Ollie\u2019s Bargain Outlet Holdings (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OLLI\" title=\"Ollie's Bargain Outlet Holdings, Inc.\">OLLI</a>), and Academy Sports and Outdoors (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASO\" title=\"Academy Sports and Outdoors, Inc.\">ASO</a>). </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\"><span>See the full earnings calendar</span></a><span>.</span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>Earnings spotlight:</span><span> </span></strong><span>Wednesday, December 11 - Adobe. </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\"><span>See the full earnings calendar</span></a><span>.</span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>Earnings spotlight:</span></strong><span> Thursday, December 12 - Broadcom, Costco Wholesale, and Ciena. </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/earnings/earnings-calendar#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\"><span>See the full earnings calendar</span></a><span>.</span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>Volatility Watch: </span><span></span></strong><span>The most overbought stocks per their 14-day relative strength index include HUMBL (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HMBL\" title=\"HUMBL, Inc.\">OTCPK:HMBL</a>) and Oriental Rise (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORIS\" title=\"Oriental Rise Holdings Limited\">ORIS</a>). The most oversold stocks per their 14-day Relative Strength Index include Imperial Petroleum (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IMPP\" title=\"Imperial Petroleum Inc.\">IMPP</a>) and Cellectar Biosciences (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CLRB\" title=\"Cellectar Biosciences, Inc.\">CLRB</a>). Short interest is elevated on B. Riley (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RILY\" title=\"B. Riley Financial, Inc.\">RILY</a>) and Medical Properties Trust (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MPW\" title=\"Medical Properties Trust, Inc.\">MPW</a>).</span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>IPO Watch: </span></strong><span></span><span>ServiceTitan (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TTAN\" title=\"ServiceTitan, Inc.\">TTAN</a>) is expected to price its $501.6M IPO on Wednesday and to begin trading on Thursday. The lockup for Tempus AI (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TEM\" title=\"Tempus AI, Inc\">TEM</a>) will expire on Wednesday. </span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>Dividend Watch: </span></strong><span></span><span>Companies that have an ex-dividend coming next week include</span><span> Alphabet (GOOG, GOOGL), UnitedHealth (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNH\" title=\"UnitedHealth Group Incorporated\">UNH</a>), FedEx (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FDX\" title=\"FedEx Corporation\">FDX</a>), Travelers (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TRV\" title=\"The Travelers Companies, Inc.\">TRV</a></span></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742721-oracle-and-broadcom-are-top-names-reporting-results-as-earning-season-winds-down", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 19:00:00"}, {"id": "4742467", "title": "Strathcona Resources: Attractive Exposure To The Oil Price", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Oil refinery and\u200b industrial\u200b city\u200b After sunset\" data-id=\"1143972969\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143972969/image_1143972969.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">pugun-photo</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>I have been following Strathc