/s3/uploads/getty_images/166446682/image_166446682.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/166446682/image_166446682.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/166446682/image_166446682.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/166446682/image_166446682.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/166446682/image_166446682.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">da-kuk/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-authored by Treading Softly.</em></p> <blockquote> <p>\"The night is darkest just before the dawn\"</p> <p><em>\u2013 Harvey Dent.</em></p> </blockquote> <p>Have you ever noticed that when navigating at night\u2014perhaps with no light source apart from the natural glow of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/166446682/image_166446682.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742646-i-am-loading-up-on-this-fat-11-percent-yield-apollo-commercial", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 18:30:00"}, {"id": "4742818", "title": "Bitcoin: Empirical Evidence And Fundamentals Call For Higher Prices", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract bitcoin concept\" data-id=\"2138995594\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">koto_feja</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Bitcoin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTC-USD\" title=\"Bitcoin USD\">BTC-USD</a>) recently surpassed the $100,000 mark for the first time ever, proving naysayers wrong. I do not own Bitcoin, but I have exposure to cryptocurrencies through my investment in Coinbase Global Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COIN\" title=\"Coinbase Global, Inc.\">COIN</a>). Bitcoin</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2138995594/image_2138995594.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742818-bitcoin-empirical-evidence-and-fundamentals-call-for-higher-prices", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 18:14:13"}, {"id": "4742223", "title": "Powell Industries: Don't Chase This Rally - No Margin Of Safety", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Thumbs Down (XXXL)\" data-id=\"184983574\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1205px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184983574/image_184983574.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">4FR</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2> </h2> <h2>Powell Industries: Don't Chase This Rally - Baked In Upside Triggers Downgrade</h2> <p><span>We previously covered </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718509-powell-industries-has-rarely-been-cheaper-upgrade-buy\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718509-powell-industries-has-rarely-been-cheaper-upgrade-buy\" target=\"_blank\">Powell Industries, Inc.</a><span> (NASDAQ:</span><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/POWL\" title=\"Powell Industries, Inc.\">POWL</a></span><span>) in September 2024, discussing its bright prospects attrib